{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers were experimenting with generative AI's ability to summarize information in the context of summarizing existing research for literature reviews, generating abstracts, and learning about a subject area outside of their area of expertise.",
    "However, there were vastly contrasting opinions on the utility of using AI-generated summaries in these ways due to concerns about inaccuracies.",
    "Researchers in STEM were more likely to have reported using generative AI for summarization and literature review assistance, but there were adopters and non-adopters across disciplines.",
    "Opinions around the ethics and usefulness of generative AI in these contexts circled back to a few key questions.",
    "Does using generative AI to summarize existing scholarship mean scholars are not reading and understanding that scholarship in the same way as before?"
  ]
}